creator: GaldermaUSA
descriptionHtml:
Experience Galderma's premium events and meetings through a mobile app that offers interactivity and networking. The app provides delegates with a paperless environment including:
- Networking: instant messaging with delegates, exchange of digital business cards, access to attendee lists.
- Interactivity: voting, submit questions, take surveys,
- Content and Logistics: documents, virtual library, create personal agendas and bookmarks notes, speaker profiles.
descriptionShort: Experience Galderma's events on your cell phone.
title: Galderma Events
